node.text: I’m bored and I’ve wanted to tell this story for ages

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by troye sivan on August 15, 2021 tagging @emmaconfetti, @itsmarkholland, @viktoriajuryga, and @emimusicau. May be an image of 1 person.

node.text: 7 years (!!) since i put out my first EP w @emimusicau. Planned the whole roll out on butcher paper in @viktoriajuryga’s living room w no music management or US label and didn’t expect a thing and then you guys made it #1 in 55 countries and changed my life foreverrrrrrr. Happy Little Pill is still my mum’s ringtone for me lol. Love you guyth ❤️

node.text: I wrote this song crying in my kitchen just as life started to fall apart a bit. Recorded the vocal there n then, and put it as an interlude on the EP. now..surprise! 🥸 could cry just thinking about you (Full Version) is out on all streaming platforms 💜 saddest song ever but we okay now. Sorta 🤣🤣🤣 Love you
Digital art collection called BL00M2021, just dropped on @niftygateway in collaboration with @jasonebeyer. Raising money for @glaad 😚 very excited about this. Cop one for the LGBTQs if you want
